{"tid":250790,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)天煞西部反撃戰 波士BB LEGO蝙蝠俠 高度反擊","createTime":"2017-05-20T11:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T18:41:49.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae1f97edb934d7b933d6975df9593adefab90b5c","tid":250790,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:04:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=8c65eac9\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=fb4046a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=967b5d3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/ff/Cowboys_%26_Aliens.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Fff%2FCowboys_%2526_Aliens.jpg&h=a657b7b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/40/The-boss-baby.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F40%2FThe-boss-baby.jpg&h=4674de08&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i1.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/original/001/220/625/e2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Foriginal%2F001%2F220%2F625%2Fe2f.jpg&h=39acf7b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/xSysuKP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxSysuKP.jpg&h=39f019b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/75/Enemy_of_the_State.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F75%2FEnemy_of_the_State.jpg&h=bdb4a770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1873年，一個左腕鎖著奇異手扣的失憶男子（丹尼爾基克 飾）突然出現在亞利桑那州的一個小鎮上。鎮上的人都對他充滿戒心，原因是他們一直被鐵腕鎮長（夏里遜福 飾）高壓統治，生活中只剩下恐慌...不過他們沒料到真正恐怖的事情竟隨之而發生，不知名的東西從天而降，以閃電的速度和奇怪的武器，無情地將鎮民一一捕獵﹗這時候失憶男子漸漸回復記憶，並想到了對付外星人的方法﹗為了生存，鎮上的民眾終於團結起來，用火藥與牛仔無比的勇氣，向外星作出終極反擊..<br />\n<br />\n2.一個穿西裝打領帶、智慧過於常人的嬰兒，來到7歲男孩的家中，憑著好口才擄獲提姆父母的關注，為這個家帶來劇烈轉變，並引發一連串有趣的故事..<br />\n<br />\n3.聯手艾密特和野女孩拯救樂高宇宙三年後，蝙蝠俠繼續他在哥譚市警惡鋤奸的事業。一次阻止小丑破壞哥譚市的任務中。蝙蝠俠告訴小丑他並沒有自己想的那麼重要，導致小丑展開針對蝙蝠俠的復仇大計。<br />\n次日，蝙蝠俠以布魯斯&middot;韋恩的身份出席城裡的冬季晚會，慶祝詹姆士&middot;高登卸任哥譚市警察局的警察總監。高登的女兒芭芭拉接替他的職位。然而，芭芭拉宣布計劃重構警察智能，拋棄蝙蝠俠。小丑帶著哥譚一眾反派本打算搞亂派對，最終屈服於警方。儘管意識到他不再有保護城市安全的任，蝙蝠俠還是懷疑他的大敵人小丑有所企圖，決定提前阻止他，欲把他扔進關押著樂高宇宙大多數反派的監獄幻影地帶..<br />\n<br />\n4.影片開頭，國會正準備通過一項立法，擴大執法機構的監聽權限。國會議員菲爾&middot;漢默斯里（Phil Hammersley，由傑森&middot;羅伯茲飾演，未署名）認為其侵犯隱私權，試圖阻止。托馬斯&middot;雷諾茲（Thomas Reynolds，強&middot;沃特飾演）則認為該法案有助於打擊恐怖分子，於是他派美國國家安全局探員大衛&middot;普萊特（David Pratt，巴里&middot;佩珀飾演）用注射器殺死漢默斯利，並偽裝成是心臟病致死<br />\n<br />\n7 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e823389dbda09351ad61a26e132a678b44a39a1","tid":250790,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd7ba39e0833147ed7e9ec291b0c2fa2aea74a9","tid":25